"Whats' Wrong with the Consumer Goods Organization?" by Armstrong, Arthur G.; Enright, Helene; Lempres, Elizabeth C.; Rauch, Stacey - The McKinsey Quarterly, Issue 1, Winter 1996 | Online Research Library: Questia






















